  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, your intensity in battle can shield you and help you strike true. As a bonus action on your turn, you can give yourself <strong>advantage </strong>on all weapon attack rolls until the end of the current turn. When you do so, you also gain <strong>5 temporary hit points</strong>. The number of hit points increases when you reach certain levels in this class, increasing to 10 at 10th level and 15 at 15th level.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature three times. You regain all expended uses of it when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
